-- Full production-station market (phase 10.18), generated by
-- cmd/starwind-tools/gen-station-markets. Widens goods_types to the full
-- StarWind catalog (the 0006 seed is a subset) and seeds station_goods for
-- every built production station (owner_kind 2) from its type's legacy
-- station_goods_types cycle: inputs are buy rows, the output is a sell row.
